comment: I don't quite understand: Wouldn't the replication method to increase fault tolerance also increase the amount of data to be stored? So for example, instead of 128MB of data (Block B) to be stored in a node, I now have 128MB x 2 amount of data to be stored in that node because I also need to store Block B AND the replica of Black A.
